{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
Evidence in prosecution for capital murder was sufficient to sustain jury\rquote s verdict finding defendant guilty, where at punishment stage of trial defendant testified, against his attorney\rquote s advice, and admitted killing the victim.
\par 
}
}
}
