{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa200 \sb0 
In reviewing sufficiency of the evidence in a criminal case, the Court of Criminal Appeals will look to all of the evidence in the case that was adduced at both stages of the trial, and not just that offered or presented by the state.
\par 
}
}
}
