{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Circumstantially, even without considering testimony of codefendant who testified for the State, evidence in prosecution for capital murder was more than sufficient to sustain guilty verdict, and would permit a rational trier of fact to find guilt beyond a reasonable doubt. 
}
