{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Capital murder defendant was not denied his right of confrontation by alleged failure to inform jury of any plea bargain agreement existing between the prosecution and defendant\rquote s accomplice, who was a witness for the State, prior to her testifying against defendant, where record reflected jury was informed that accomplice would be charged only with lesser offense of murder or offense of kidnapping, and no other agreement existed at time of defendant\rquote s trial. 
}
