{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ri30 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li30 
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
There is no constitutional requirement that a codefendant who testifies for the prosecution in capital murder case must receive same punishment as defendant receives, even if that is the death sentence, nor is there any constitutional requirement that a comparative proportionality review of defendant\rquote s death sentence must be made by an appellate court. 
}
