{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
Fact that accomplice of capital murder defendant, who testified for the State, received ten years\rquote  deferred probation for her participation in the abduction and murder of the victim while defendant received death sentence did not violate the Eighth Amendment to the Federal Constitution. 
}
