1
}}}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
 the evidence is more than sufficient to sustain the verdict of the jury, and would permit a rational trier of fact to find guilt beyond a reasonable doubt. Appellant\rquote s ground of error that the evidence is insufficient to sustain the capital murder verdict of the jury is overruled.
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
