{\b0 \cf1 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
. There is no constitutional requirement that a co-defendant who testifies for the prosecution must receive the same punishment as the defendant has received, nor is there any constitutional requirement that a comparative proportionality review of appellant\rquote s death sentence must be made by an appellate court. 
}
