{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://wwwtest.int.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1980122109&pubNum=713&originatingDoc=Ic2428eb5e7bc11d9b386b232635db992&refType=RP&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.History*oc.DocAnalysisJudicial)" }{\fldrslt 
