The jury was instructed that this was \u8220\'3fa case depending for conviction on circumstantial evidence,\u8221\'3f and was also instructed on the law of circumstantial evidence. In 
}
{\field {\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "http://wwwtest.int.westlaw.com/Link/Document/FullText?findType=Y&serNum=1981148112&pubNum=713&originatingDoc=Ic2428eb5e7bc11d9b386b232635db992&refType=RP&fi=co_pp_sp_713_197&originationContext=document&vr=3.0&rs=cblt1.0&transitionType=DocumentItem&contextData=(sc.History*oc.DocAnalysisJudicial)#co_pp_sp_713_197" }{\fldrslt 
{\b0 \cf25 \f5 \i1 \fs20 
