{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li400 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
\u8220\'3f(b) On conclusion of the presentation of the evidence, the court shall submit the following issues to the jury:
\par 
}
}
}
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf1 \f5 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li400 
